Title: AS FOR ME I WILL BEHOLD THY FACE IN  RIGHTEOUSNESS (至于我我必在义中得见你的面 特.)
CCLI: 735

Verse 1 English:
IRREGULAR METER
Psalms and Scripture Portions
As for me, I will behold Thy face in righteousness,
I will be satisfied when I awake with Thy likeness.
I want to be just like You, Lord,
So as for me, I will behold Thy face.
So as for me, I will behold Thy face.

Verse 1 Chinese:
